{"tid":445957,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人走左，身後事應該點搞","createTime":"2017-10-24T01:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T06:00:00.000Z","uid":51056,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"eb934d20587b542361ad5e3407313889d37c76f7","tid":445957,"uid":51056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:17:58.000Z","msg":"爸爸琴晚係醫院走左<br />\n而家要等醫院打黎拎死亡證<br />\n想知爸爸d身後事既過程係點。。因為無經驗<br />\n咩頭七三七個d 上網睇完都唔係好明個次序同要做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爸爸偏向信佛既 所以設靈應該用返中式個種<br />\n<br />\n巴絲有無人做呢行/有經驗教下我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72c76e813e282c69d64a47994819ecd5d8edf08","tid":445957,"uid":51056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c287ba04da0727123ebca3b002e1fdbd60f0de55","tid":445957,"uid":29742,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"冇殯儀sales搵你咩？佢地所有野都會教曬你仲跟得好足"},{"pid":"ae92f1fe624b976906ccb06c3c9cf44ef34c02af","tid":445957,"uid":29742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:27:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇殯儀sales搵你咩？佢地所有野都會教曬你仲跟得好足</blockquote><br />\n我前年屋企有人過身，佢地會響一d必經之路又唔會好阻掟既地方等客，雖然價錢唔平，但做得好足跟得好足，總之做完所有野全家都安心放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ab847830159f7efac82569ec5373c760cd47be","tid":445957,"uid":51056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇殯儀sales搵你咩？佢地所有野都會教曬你仲跟得好足</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽朋友講個d人未必信得過<br />\n所以搵緊d朋友幫<br />\n但爸爸份人好簡單<br />\n可能醫院設靈都ok<br />\n不過唔知d儀式係咪都要搵人黎醫院搞。。"},{"pid":"f8ff2553ad56a13a6504e21cbff8c34d1e1835d8","tid":445957,"uid":51056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇殯儀sale